        "body": "A dental and imaging group needs a radiology technician with a specific state certification, a role that has historically sat open for months at a time with almost no qualified applicants surfacing through the usual channels. Aster flags the handful of applicants whose resumes list the exact credential, with the reasons attached to the score so nothing has to be taken on faith, and self-scheduling gets a first interview booked the same day a strong match appears, cutting the gap between application and interview that used to stall these niche, hard-to-source searches for months at a time."
